cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.DL

This paper discusses the design and implementation of smart contract templates, which involves aspects of cryptography (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), and deep learning (cs.DL). However, since the paper focuses more on the technical aspects of smart contract templates, we believe that cs.CR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories, followed by cs.PL, cs.SE, and cs.DL.
